data.description: Welcome to this stunning, modern home that offers luxury, comfort, and functionality throughout. Step inside the grand foyer and be captivated by the elegance of wood floors and high ceilings that create an open and airy atmosphere. The heart of the home is the great room with gas fireplace, built-in ceiling speakers, and a wall of windows looking out over open space to the mountains. The gourmet kitchen features beautiful cabinetry, stainless steel appliances including double ovens and gas range top, spacious pantry, and a large granite island with seating. A sunny breakfast nook walks out to the covered patio for alfresco dining or enjoying the Colorado sunsets. The formal dining room with oversized custom barn doors offers an elegant dining space. The main-level master suite is tucked away with it's spa-like 5 pc bath and large walk-in closet with direct access to the laundry room. A second bedroom and bathroom up front offer a space for guests. The lower level can be another living space all to itself with huge family room with electric fireplace, game area, dining or office area, and kitchenette with wet bar and dishwasher. There are three bedrooms and two bathrooms in the lower level including the junior master suite with private bath and walk-in closets. The huge oversized 4-car garage offers plenty of space for a workshop. Other special amenities of this home include a 10x14 storage shed, fenced back yard, 3-zone drip system, and much more! Meridian Ranch community has a clubhouse with pool, open spaces with playgrounds and parks, and convenient location near dining and shopping.
